This paper proposes a new method to evaluate GANs, which is a popular topic in machine learning and computer vision. The paper focuses on evaluating the reconstruction quality and likelihood of GANs, which are important metrics in the field of generative models. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, since the paper deals with GANs, which are a type of neural network, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible sub-category. Finally, since the paper proposes a new evaluation method, cs.GR (Graphics) could also be a relevant sub-category.
